              <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                Saya fokus di operasi ISP/NOC: routing, PPPoE, bandwidth management, monitoring, dan otomatisasi.
                Tujuan saya: jaringan stabil, troubleshooting cepat, dan tooling yang bisa dipakai tim.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                <a href="#projects" class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-cyan-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-all">
